page.title: 12Cliff Park Housing Estate.
page.content: This estate is a planned housing estate. It is a mixture of bungalow & houses. The houses are detached, semi-detached & in terraces. A feature of this estate is the area called "Mariner's Compass. "This is a road built in a large circle with other roads, paths & passages leading off it at various points of the compass. The names of some of the roads are to do with the sea for example "Bowters", "Humber Keel" & "Newton Cross" there being areas of sea off the coast. The estate has fascilities such as two shops & a pub. There are 4 schools Cliff Park Infants, Middle & High schools & St Edmunds R.C. school
